<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <title>Laurent RAYMOND - Game Designer</title>

    <meta name="description" content="Game designer for multiplayer and puzzle games"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/png" href="favicon-16x16.png"/>

    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bulma/0.7.4/css/bulma.min.css" rel="preload" as="style" onload="this.rel='stylesheet'">
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.7.2/css/all.min.css" rel="preload" as="style" onload="this.rel='stylesheet'">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:300,400" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.datatables.net/v/dt/jq-3.3.1/dt-1.10.18/datatables.min.css"  rel="preload" as="style" onload="this.rel='stylesheet'"/>
    <link href="style.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>


<body>

<section class="hero is-fullheight video">
  <!-- Hero head: will stick at the top -->
  <div class="hero-head">
    <nav class="navbar">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-brand">
          <a class="navbar-item">
            GAME DEVELOPMENT
          </a>
          <span class="navbar-burger burger" data-target="navbarMenuHeroA">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
          </span>
        </div>

      </div>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-video">
    <video poster="img/bgimg.jpg" id="bgvid" playsinline autoplay muted loop>
        <!-- <source src="vid/BGvid.webm" type="video/webm"> -->
        <source src="header.mp4" type="video/mp4">
    </video>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero content: will be in the middle -->
  <div class="hero-body">
    <div class="container has-text-centered">
      <h1 class="title has-text-weight-light" style="font-size:5rem">
        Laurent RAYMOND
      </h1>
      <h2 class="subtitle has-text-weight-light" style="font-size:3rem">
        Game Designer
      </h2>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero footer: will stick at the bottom -->
  <div class="hero-foot">
  <div class="buttons are-large is-centered" style="padding-bottom: 2rem">
      <a class="button is-black" href="#about" style="background-color: #4bb8e7">About</a>
      <a class="button is-black" href="#portfolio" style="background-color: #4bb8e7">Portfolio</a>
      <a class="button is-black" href="#cv" style="background-color: #4bb8e7">CV</a>
      <a class="button is-black" href="#contact" style="background-color: #4bb8e7">Contact</a>
      </div>

  </div>
</section>


<section class="section has-background-black-ter passion" id="about">

<div class="tile is-ancestor">
  <div class="tile is-7 is-vertical is-parent">

    <div class="tile is-child box has-background-grey-dark has-text-white-ter">
      <p class="title has-text-weight-light has-text-white-ter">Tech</p>
      <p>I've been developing games in haxe, javascript, Lua, Python and in game engines such as Unity and Godot Engine but my expertise is in the <b>Haxe</b> language, 
      as i can <b>target any platform</b> and makes porting as3 (flash) games to web or desktop fast.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tile is-child box  has-background-grey-dark has-text-white-ter">
      <p class="title has-text-weight-light has-text-white-ter">Games</p>
      <p>I've invested much of my time into multiplayer online games with strong emphasis on the mechanics. <b>I am now doing puzzle and educational games for the web and mobile.</b></p>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="tile is-parent">
    <div class="tile is-child box has-background-grey-dark has-text-white-ter">
      <p class="title has-text-weight-light has-text-white-ter">Me</p>
      <figure class="image is-128x128 is-pulled-left" style="padding-right:1rem">
        <img class="is-rounded" src="me.jpg">
      </figure>
      <p>After my first steps in python i decided to invest my time into game development. I made many multiplayer online prototypes, participated into game jams and worked on many games.
      I set on minimalistic puzzle games, sometimes targeted at children. I keep only the raw mechanic in my games.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

</section>



<section class="section has-background-black-ter" id="portfolio">
<div class="container">

  <h1 class="title has-text-centered has-text-grey has-text-weight-light is-size-1">Porfolio</h1>

  {% for game in y.games %}

  {% if loop.index0 %3 == 0 %}
  <div class="columns is-centered">
  {% endif %}

    <div class="column">
      <div id="{{ game.title }}" class="card is-shady has-background-grey-darker has-text-grey-lighter has-equal-height">

        <header class="card-header">
          <p class="card-header-title is-size-2 has-text-weight-light is-centered has-text-light">
            {{ game.title }}
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="card-image has-text-centered">
          <figure class="image">

            <video poster="dummy.jpg" playsinline autoplay muted loop>
                <!-- <source src="vid/BGvid.webm" type="video/webm"> -->
                <source src="{{ game.video }}" type="video/mp4">
            </video>
            
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="card-content has-text-centered">
            <div class="content is-medium">
                <span class="is-size-3 has-text-weight-light">{{ game.genre }}</span>
                <p>{{ game.description }}
                </p>

                {% if game.title == "Ukubala" %}
                <em>Project in progress</em><br/><br/>
                <a href="ukubala/index.html" class="button is-large is-info">Try now</a>
                {% endif %}
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
   
  {% if loop.index % 3 == 2 or loop.last %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}
  {% endfor %}

</div>
</section>

<section class="hero is-info is-bold" id="cv">
  <div class="hero-body has-text-centered">
    <h1 class="title has-text-weight-light is-size-1">Curriculum Vitae</h1>
    <a href="https://www.dropbox.com/s/4sf0o56jzshywja/Game%20Designer%20-%20Laurent%20RAYMOND.pdf?raw=1" class="button is-large has-text-weight-light">View as pdf &nbsp;<i class="fas fa-file"></i></a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="hero is-light is-bold" id="contact">
<div class="hero-body has-text-centered">
<h1 class="title has-text-weight-light is-size-1">Contact</h1>
<p>laurent.rd@gmail.com</p>
</div>
</section>
